data.description: 118 Bermuda is a 3 bed, 2 bath home that has been remodeled with tons of gorgeous, modern finishes. The kitchen boasts beautiful tile backsplash, double wall ovens, and an eat-in breakfast nook. The main bathroom features a full tile shower with glass shower door, tiled floors, and an elegant vanity with a vessel sink. The spacious master has a full en suite bathroom as well! Outside there's a sprawling fenced backyard with a massive storage shed with an attached screened-in patio. There's a possibility to convert the building in the back to an ADU for supplemental income. Best of all this home comes FULLY FURNISHED! This home would make an excellent investment property for short, mid, or long term rentals. This property is also located in a no City Tax area, and the property has no HOA. Schedule your showing of this unique property today!
